data.description: This very comfortable home has an open floor plan and spacious feel. Only 1 block from Lake Weatherford, close to the new boardwalk and Lake Weatherford boat ramp.  Split bedrooms, large living room with cozy fireplace, fresh paint, and great quiet neighborhood. With a fenced backyard, and covered back porch, come home and relax. Walk to the lake. See the lake when the tree drop their leaves! Such a perfect location, close to Weatherford, but without the traffic and noise. Only 30 minutes to downtown Fort Worth. Minutes from shopping and restaurants in Weatherford. Professional pictures coming Saturday.
